# Cashback App Rules

- Main flow lives in `components/cashback-app.tsx` (`empty → gallery → bank-select → processing → results`).
- Static data: `lib/cashback-data.ts` (`BANKS`, `MARKETS`, `CASHBACK_ROWS`, tiers).
- Mobile-first; phone shell on `sm:` breakpoints.
- Russian copy; tier colors: green/yellow/red for cashback rates.
- Use Framer Motion for screen transitions (`AnimatePresence`, 0.35s).
